- Removed extraneous metadata footnote (`Presented at the First Maximum Entropy Workshop...`) from the file.
- Fixed one introduced duplicate Stage 2 equation line during QA pass.

Self-check completed:
- Intended paragraph boundaries are blank-line separated where adjusted.
- No unresolved in-text equation references to missing display-equation numbers remain.
